id: pm-naiv
title: pm install exits 0 on error (CRITICAL agent-blocker)
description: "Dogfood 2026-05-17: `pm install` (bare) and `pm install <bad-name>` print error text but exit with code 0, misleading agents into believing the install succeeded. Found in dogfood session 12.\n\nRepro: `pm init && pm install nonexistent-name; echo exit=$?` -> prints Error: but exits 0.\n\nFix: install command must propagate non-zero exit codes on failure. Check src/cli/commands/extension.ts and src/cli/commands/package.ts install handlers."
type: Issue
status: closed
priority: 0
tags[5]: agent-ux,bug,cli,exit-code,install
created_at: "2026-05-17T06:47:13.035Z"
